Package Compiler.ErrorHandling

Class UnderlineErrorListener

java.lang.Object
org.antlr.v4.runtime.BaseErrorListener
Compiler.ErrorHandling.UnderlineErrorListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
BuffErrorListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.ANTLRErrorListener
public class UnderlineErrorListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.BaseErrorListener
implements BuffErrorListener
An error listener that can be used by both ANTLR generated components as the parser and lexer and custom listeners/visitors to print out underlined error messages to the console.sssssd
